SEAHUNT -1x23- LEGEND OF THE MERMAID  (6/14/1958)

While helping his sponge diving friends Marie and Alex Curous off the West coast of Florida near Tarpon Springs, Mike hears bells and is sucked toward a cave.  Escaping the current, Mike employs a "diver&#039;s parachute" while dropping his weight belt to return to the surface.  Learning about the myth of a mermaid, Mike is strangely drawn to investigate the cave again.

Starring Lloyd Bridges as Mike Nelson
Guest Stars: Larry Hagman (Alex Curous), Regina Gleason (Marie Curous), Paul Fierro (Nick Demitrias)
Original airdate: 14 June 1958
Underwater Sequences filmed in Silver Springs Florida
